INSERT INTO ims_document_chapter_content (id, chapter_id, content,layout) VALUES(  '1056', '1834', '## 返回值
```php
$this->result($errno, $message, $data)
```
- $errno 错误码，0为成功，非0有表示有错误
- $message 错误信息或是成功信息
- $data 返回的数据

### 示例
```php
$this->result(0, \'登录成功\', array(\'uid\' => 1235));

//输出
{\"errno\":0,\"message\":\"\",\"data\":{\"test\":1235}}
```', '1' ); 
