INSERT INTO ims_document_chapter_content (id, chapter_id, content,layout) VALUES(  '1651', '2763', '##说明

###http

http-client采用的是guzzle的http客户端,配置参数和guzzle保持一致
请求方法：post,get,head,delete,options,put
参考文档：https://guzzle-cn.readthedocs.io/zh_CN/latest/

```
namespace W7\\Rpc;

$client = new Rpc([
	\'ba<x>se_uri\' => \'http://127.0.0.1\'
]);
$ret = $client->post(\'test/url\', [
	\'form_params\' => [
		\'key\' => \'value\'
	]
]);

//这里获取到的response即guzzle http-client返回的response
$response = $client->getResponse();
```


###tcp
采用的tcp客户端为swoole_client，用法请参考swoole_client
数据的传输方式目前支持：JSON，thrift-binary
请求方法：post,get,head,delete,options,put **兼容http形式**
参考文档：https://wiki.swoole.com/wiki/page/p-client.html


#####thrift-binary

```
namespace W7\\Rpc;

$client = new Rpc([
	\'ba<x>se_uri\' => \'tcp-thrift://127.0.0.1:8888\'
]);
$ret = $client->get(\'test/url\');
```

#####JSON
```
namespace W7\\Rpc;

$client = new Rpc([
	\'ba<x>se_uri\' => \'tcp://127.0.0.1:8888\'
]);
$ret = $client->post(\'test/url\', [
	\'key\' => \'value\'
