INSERT INTO ims_document_chapter_content (id, chapter_id, content,layout) VALUES(  '1824', '3005', '###说明
调试工具不区分当前开发环境, 调用调试工具后,后续的执行流程将终止, 直接向客户端返回调试信息

###调用方式
```
idd(\'data\', $data);
```

###示例
```
namespace W7\\App\\Controller;

use W7\\Core\\Controller\\ControllerAbstract;
use W7\\Http\\Message\\Server\\Request;

class HomeController extends ControllerAbstract {
	public function dd(Request $request) {
		$data = [
			\'uid\' => 1,
			\'username\' => \'rangine\'
		];

		idd($data, $request);

		return $data;
	}
}
```
执行结果

![](//cdn.w7.cc/images/2019/07/18/15634324385d3015f737671_F1UITX1tkXtt.png)

如果需要美化输出结果, 可安装symfony/var-dumper(目前只支持该方式)
```
composer require symfony/var-dumper
```
美化后的结果

![](//cdn.w7.cc/images/2019/07/18/15634325975d3016966a654_sprP4SwwRWLJ.png)', '1' ); 
INSERT INTO ims_document_chapter_content (id, chapter_id, content,layout) VALUES(  '1825', '2506', '###说明
1. 验证器的使用方式和规则和laravel的用法一致,具体可查看laravel的[validate](https://learnku.com/docs/laravel/5.5/validation/1302 \"validate\")使用方式
2. validate支持语言包, 会自动翻译为设定的语言, 语言包配置在config/lang/ 下 如果设置的语言为zh-CN  完整路径为config/lang/zh-CN/validation.php
3. 在非controller中，可以调用ivalidate()方法进行数据检测
###使用
```
$this->validate($request, [
	\'name\' => \'required\',
	\'password\' => \'required\'
]);
```

###示例
```
namespace W7\\App\\Controller;

use W7\\Core\\Controller\\ControllerAbstract;
use W7\\Http\\Message\\Server\\Request;

class HomeController extends ControllerAbstract {
	public function login(Request $request) {
		$this->validate($request, [
			\'name\' => \'required\',
			\'password\' => \'required\'
		]);
		
		//也可以指定具体的错误信息
		/*
		$this->validate($request, [
			\'name\' => \'required\',
			\'password\' => \'required\'
		], [
			\'name.required\' => \'请输入用户姓名\',
			\'password.required\' => \'请输入用户密码\'
		]);
		*/

		$data = [
			\'uid\' => 1,
			\'username\' => \'rangine\'
		];

		return $data;
	}
}
```

执行结果

![](//cdn.w7.cc/images/2019/07/18/15634343715d301d83f3875_QOo8e993ib3I.png)', '1' ); 
