自定义handler需要继承W7\\Core\\Cache\\Handler\\HandlerAbstract
自定义handler中不需要对数据进行encode或者decode处理，底层会进行数据处理接管

###配置
如果需要修改默认的缓存, 直接修改cache/default/driver配置为自定义handler的名称即可
```
return [
    \'cache\' => [
        \'memory\' => [
			//这里的test 就是上述的${Name}
            \'driver\' => \'test\'
        ]
    ]
]
```

###编写handler
可通过执行命令创建
```
bin/gerent make:handler  --name=test --type=cache
```
执行成功后会在app/handler/cache/下创建TestHandler文件
```
namespace W7\\App\\Handler\\Cache;

use W7\\Core\\Cache\\Handler\\HandlerAbstract;

class TestHandler extends HandlerAbstract {
	private static $data;

	public static function getHandler($config): HandlerAbstract {
		//框架会使用这里返回的实例进行缓存处理
		return new static();
	}

	public function set($key, $value, $ttl = null) {
		if ($ttl <= 0) {
			$ttl = 9999999999;
		}
		self::$data[$key] = [
			\'value\' => $value,
			\'expires\' => time() + $ttl
		];
	}

	public function get($key, $default = null) {
		if (!isset(self::$data[$key])) {
			return $default;
		}
		if (self::$data[$key][\'expires\'] < time()) {
			$this->delete($key);
			return $default;
		}
		return self::$data[$key][\'value\'];
	}

	public function has($key) {
		$data = $this->get($key);
		return $data !== null ? true : false;
	}

	public function setMultiple($values, $ttl = null) {
		foreach ($values as $key => $value) {
			$this->set($key, $value, $ttl);
		}
	}

	public function getMultiple($keys, $default = null) {
		$values = [];
		foreach ($keys as $index => $name) {
			$values[] = $this->get($name, $default);
		}

		return $values;
	}

	public function delete($key) {
		unset(self::$data[$key]);
	}

	public function deleteMultiple($keys) {
		foreach ($keys as $index => $name) {
			$this->delete($name);
		}
	}

	public function clear() {
		self::$data = [];
	}
}
```
